---
title: Asian Tofu & Peanut Sauce Tacos with Creamy Sesame Slaw & Plant-Based Mayonnaise
description: What happens when you combine the flavours of Mexico and Asia into one dish? A whole new take on tacos you
didn’t know you needed! Golden tofu and creamy sesame slaw are nestled into a warm tortilla, then drizzled with a
delightfully nutty peanut sauce. Yum!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with spring onion due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6661519e5d2e087e51dbfdd5-08f9e368.jpeg
